Key Match Events: Andrew Wiggins tallied 18 points in the third quarter on 8-of-7 shooting from the field with three made 3-pointers
Miscellaneous Highlights: Six different members of the Warriors tallied 11 or more points against the Grizzlies
Others: Dennis Schroder notched his highest-scoring performance as a Warrior, scoring 17 points on 6-of-15 shooting from the field to go along with nine assists and three rebounds in 36 minutes
